        {
            "id": 6125563,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 德康醫療(DXCM-US)大跌5.02%，報78.13美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>德康醫療(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DXCM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DXCM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DXCM-US</a>)截至台北時間25日22:02股價下跌4.13美元，報78.13美元，跌幅5.02%，成交量521,390（股），盤中最高價82.20美元、最低價78.13美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.36%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.15%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.06%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-0.09%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>德康醫療(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DXCM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DXCM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DXCM-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+1.62%</li> <li>近 1 月：-5.16%</li> <li>近 3 月：-2.66%</li> <li>近 6 月：-9.36%</li> <li>今年以來：+5.77%</li></ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6125563",
